Since Psychic Progenitor and Complete Cloaking were mentioned, I'd like to make one correction to my guide. I completly missed the fact that Bosalian Genetic Throwback also provides Complete Cloaking, at level 20. <br />
<br />
Also, next update abilities will change a bit:<br />
- increase per-level will be more linear, making low- and mid-level admirals much better<br />
- most abilities will come earlier<br />
- some useless abilities are improved<br />
<br />
This will help non mega-council who can't train their level 20 commies by sacrificing production or invading the empire. The difference between level 20 and lower levels won't be so mad anymore.			   <P align=right></P>
